These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, electronic
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of electronic is not to the right of the fan of electronic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: horse, lizard
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
3. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | horse | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, tram
1. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | boat | tram |

 #################################

 
